data.description: Beautifully renovated craftsman style home! Situated in an established Visalia neighborhood this home surely catches the eye with its manicured landscaping.  Entering this home you are welcomed by pristine hardwood flooring and natural lighting from the large picture window in the main entertainment room. As you proceed further you reach the modernized kitchen with a little pizazz! Enjoy preparing for guests with the stainless steel appliances. There's no shortage in elegance with the quartz counters and custom cabinetry all while keeping functionality a prime key point.  Enjoy the fresh crisp water from any tap in the home courtesy of the whole house filtration system! There are also 2 spacious bedrooms with one featuring its own secluded bathroom while keeping a beautifully updated one for guests. Entering the rear exterior of the home you have a large deck  overlooking the park-like landscape. This home also features a 1 car garage that is Also Plumbed with Hot & Cold Water that's perfect to make a Studio Suite. Its also equipped with a carport for extra parking space as PPA solar to minimize those energy bills!
